'Course you could,
Lil.

289
00:09:15,956 --> 00:09:17,586
I can keep a secret.

290
00:09:17,625 --> 00:09:19,055
Lily, don't
make me laugh.

291
00:09:19,092 --> 00:09:20,392
I'd trust you
with a secret

292
00:09:20,427 --> 00:09:22,257
