299
00:09:34,808 --> 00:09:35,738
Does Marshall
shave his back?

300
00:09:35,776 --> 00:09:37,776
No, I shave it
for him. Damn it!

301
00:09:37,811 --> 00:09:38,781
Ooh!

302
00:09:38,812 --> 00:09:40,112
I should call
Marshall.

303
00:09:40,147 --> 00:09:41,577
I bet he's
in on this.

304
00:09:41,615 --> 00:09:43,575
If he really exists.

305
00:09:44,952 --> 00:09:46,422
Okay.

306
00:09:46,453 --> 00:09:47,663
Setting aside the fact

307
00:09:47,688 --> 00:09:48,988
that I've kept your whole

308
00:09:49,022 --> 00:09:51,222
"moving to Chicago" thing
a secret,

309
00:09:51,258 --> 00:09:54,088
aren't you supposed to be
dressed like Liberace right now?

310
00:09:54,127 --> 00:09:55,627
Okay, first of all,

311
00:09:55,663 --> 00:09:57,333
if I showed up in costume,

312
00:09:57,364 --> 00:09:59,074
it would steal from
the surprise and spectacle

313
00:09:59,099 --> 00:10:00,499
of my grand entrance.

314
00:10:00,533 --> 00:10:02,173
