is easy, but...

317
00:10:06,774 --> 00:10:10,414
Uh, yes, 4/4, E-sharp...

318
00:10:10,443 --> 00:10:13,783
major...

319
00:10:13,814 --> 00:10:15,484
Okay.

320
00:10:15,515 --> 00:10:18,945
Let's make something
beautiful, shall we?

321
00:10:18,986 --> 00:10:21,486
(inhales deeply)

322
