324
00:10:27,627 --> 00:10:29,957
We're gonna "run out" of ice,

325
00:10:29,997 --> 00:10:31,967
and Robin's gonna ask me
to go get some,

326
00:10:31,999 --> 00:10:34,529
and lo and behold,
the only place that sells ice

