338
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:02,159
Huh? What do we do?

339
00:11:02,195 --> 00:11:04,795
Well, I guess I could go get
some ice.

340
00:11:04,832 --> 00:11:05,972
Uh, no,
they'll send someone.

341
00:11:05,999 --> 00:11:07,669
All right, fine.
Twist my arm. I'll do it.

342
00:11:07,701 --> 00:11:08,671
But seriously,
Hmm?

343
00:11:08,702 --> 00:11:10,642
did you get everything set up
over there?

344
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:12,310
Do you have enough food,
have enough guns?

345
00:11:12,339 --> 00:11:14,809
Did you get a vest extender
for Grandma Stinson? She's...

346
00:11:14,842 --> 00:11:17,312
What are you
talking about?

347
00:11:17,344 --> 00:11:21,414
Oh, babe, you're so good
at this. I love it.

348
00:11:21,448 --> 00:11:23,248
All right, I'll see you guys
over there.

349
00:11:23,283 --> 00:11:24,823
I mean, be right back.

350
00:11:24,852 --> 00:11:28,592
Barney, Barney, this is
our rehearsal dinner, okay?

351
00:11:28,621 --> 00:11:30,361
Do not leave the premises.

352
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:32,090
Promise me you're not going
anywhere.

353
00:11:32,125 --> 00:11:33,155
Fine.

354
00:11:33,193 --> 00:11:33,933
Say it.

355
00:11:33,961 --> 00:11:36,501
Say you promise
you won't leave.

356
00:11:36,529 --> 00:11:39,929
I promise I won't leave.

357
00:11:39,967 --> 00:11:42,097
So I left.
And what do you know,

358
00:11:42,135 --> 00:11:46,165
the ice store is right next
to a laser tag place!

359
00:11:46,206 --> 00:11:48,506
No, it isn't!
It's six miles away

360
00:11:48,541 --> 00:11:49,711
in the opposite direction.

361
00:11:49,743 --> 00:11:51,543
And I told you not to go!

362
00:11:51,578 --> 00:11:52,778
Yeah, well, you also told me

363
00:11:52,813 --> 00:11:54,683
