at the wedding.

364
00:11:54,714 --> 00:11:55,624
Ring bear-er!

365
00:11:55,648 --> 00:11:56,718
We all know how great

366
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:57,850
that's gonna be. The point is,

367
00:11:57,885 --> 00:11:59,285
I played along with her plan,

368
00:11:59,319 --> 00:12:02,889
and I acted "natural" so I
wouldn't spoil the surprise.

369
00:12:02,923 --> 00:12:05,693
Oh, my goodness!

370
00:12:05,725 --> 00:12:07,555
Laser tag?!

371
00:12:07,594 --> 00:12:09,634
Maybe I should go in here
for a minute,

372
00:12:09,662 --> 00:12:11,262
