for no apparent reason.

373
00:12:11,298 --> 00:12:12,898
And what's this?

374
00:12:12,933 --> 00:12:15,443
My hands-free token satchel?

375
00:12:15,468 --> 00:12:17,808
And my free lifetime refill
root beer mug?

376
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:22,210
So for the past
two months

377
00:12:22,242 --> 00:12:24,242
when we were letting you use
our apartment

378
00:12:24,277 --> 00:12:26,077
to practice the piano
every Sunday night,

379
00:12:26,113 --> 00:12:27,583
