380
00:12:27,614 --> 00:12:31,624
Oh, so that's not traveling
'cause he's the MVP?

381
00:12:31,651 --> 00:12:34,451
Come on!

382
00:12:34,487 --> 00:12:37,057
Where's Barney?
Has anyone seen him?

383
00:12:37,090 --> 00:12:38,460
Robin, Ted's totally bailing

384
00:12:38,491 --> 00:12:40,461
on playing the piano
for you and Barney.

385
00:12:40,493 --> 00:12:44,003
Oh, really? Ted, you didn't
have to not do that.

386
00:12:44,031 --> 00:12:45,071
But thank you.

387
00:12:45,098 --> 00:12:47,838
But he promised!
A promise is a promise.

388
00:12:47,868 --> 00:12:49,638
You can't say you're
gonna do something

389
00:12:49,669 --> 00:12:52,309
and then suddenly do something
completely different!

390
00:12:52,339 --> 00:12:54,139
Why are you getting
so worked up about this?

391
00:12:54,174 --> 00:12:57,854
Because, obviously, I'm worked
up for a different

392
00:12:57,878 --> 00:12:58,978
but somewhat similar reason.

393
00:12:59,012 --> 00:13:00,582
And someone should ask me
about it!

394
00:13:00,613 --> 00:13:03,353
I'm sorry. I don't have time
for your drama right now, Lily.

395
00:13:03,383 --> 00:13:04,623
My fiancÃ© is missing.

396
