without even asking me.

398
00:13:09,322 --> 00:13:10,992
Italy's off!

399
00:13:12,325 --> 00:13:15,795
I have time for your drama.

400
00:13:22,669 --> 00:13:26,139
So, Marshall can't go
to Italy?
Not if he wants to be a judge.

401
00:13:26,173 --> 00:13:28,483
And my Italian was getting
so good.

402
00:13:28,508 --> 00:13:31,178
It was so (speaks Italian).

403
00:13:34,848 --> 00:13:37,018
But wait, you guys already
sublet the apartment.

404
00:13:37,050 --> 00:13:38,990
You're already packed.

405
00:13:39,019 --> 00:13:41,649
Marshall already borrowed
and lost my Rosetta Stone.

406
00:13:41,688 --> 00:13:43,388
That selfish bastard!

407
00:13:43,423 --> 00:13:45,663
(phone rings)
Sorry, Lil. Hello.

408
00:13:45,692 --> 00:13:47,362
Okay, I'm mad, too.

409
00:13:47,394 --> 00:13:48,964
I should hope so.

410
00:13:48,996 --> 00:13:51,296
All of a sudden, his dream
is more important than yours?

411
00:13:51,331 --> 00:13:53,031
And he did it behind your back.

412
00:13:53,066 --> 00:13:54,296
Bastardo!

413
00:13:54,334 --> 00:13:55,974
He would never hurt me
intentionally.

414
00:13:56,003 --> 00:13:57,703
I'll hurt him intentionally.

415
00:13:57,737 --> 00:13:59,007
Molto bastardo!

416
00:13:59,039 --> 00:14:00,339
That's sweet of you to say.

417
00:14:00,373 --> 00:14:02,483
You could never take
Marshall in a million years,

418
00:14:02,509 --> 00:14:04,409
but that's sweet of you to say.

419
00:14:04,444 --> 00:14:08,424
Well, apparently, Barney went
to the laser tag place

420
00:14:08,448 --> 00:14:11,048
