until the police arrive

425
00:14:20,293 --> 00:14:23,033
I need your apple juice.

426
00:14:24,197 --> 00:14:26,897
Ha!

427
00:14:26,934 --> 00:14:28,344
And here we are.

428
00:14:28,368 --> 00:14:32,238
Now, I believe this charade
has gone on long enough.

429
00:14:32,272 --> 00:14:35,912
Can we please get to the
surprise laser tag rehearsal?

430
00:14:35,943 --> 00:14:38,453
