laser tag rehearsal dinner!

431
00:14:38,478 --> 00:14:42,278
Okay, but if I may offer
an opposing view.

432
00:14:42,315 --> 00:14:43,945
Of course there is!

433
00:14:43,984 --> 00:14:46,224
This place is lousy
with clues.

434
00:14:46,253 --> 00:14:49,693
Is he even really
a security guard?

435
00:14:49,722 --> 00:14:52,262
Because he looks an awful lot
like a non-Pakistani version

436
00:14:52,292 --> 00:14:55,232
