Bring it.

517
00:18:45,225 --> 00:18:52,525
* And swore she'd also
never get married *

518
00:18:52,565 --> 00:18:55,865
* She really thought
she meant it. *

519
00:18:59,739 --> 00:19:02,009
I can't believe
